Well, It isn't super usefull, but maby someone else can find a use for it. Basicly what it does is it finds the fightstyle you use and writes it in the debug box.

[code]Procedure FindFightStyle;
var fstyle : string;
begin
gametab(1);
  if findcolor(x, y, 2106253,574,252,639,292) then
  fstyle:='attack';
  if findcolor(x, y, 2106253,659,252,724,292) then
  fstyle:='strength';
  if findcolor(x, y, 2106253,574,305,639,344) then
  fstyle:='controlled';
  if findcolor(x, y, 2106253,659,305,720,344) then
  fstyle:='defence';
writeln(fstyle);
end;[/code]
